-- For start, it is agreed that we would have our own SystemC environment at the end that will use our custom Cache models integrated with OVP virtual platforms. These
   OVP platform models will have to be encapsulated via TLM2.0 wrappers in order to be used in our environment. These OVP models would basically serve as testbench stimuli 
   to our cache model (22/09/2015)
